{"word":"ὁθούνεκα","slug":"ὁθούνεκα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁθούνεκα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>for <el>ὅτου ἕνεκα</el> as <a href='S:οὕνεκα'><el>οὕνεκα</el></a> for <el>οὗ ἕνεκα</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>because</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>οὕνεκα</el>, simply for <el>ὡς</el> or <el>ὅτι</el>, <i>that</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>quod</el>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}